<paragraph blockId="68.[160,1155,737,832]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,394,737,763]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Taxonomic history.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Morley C" box="[410,588,737,762]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" pagination="131 - 135" refId="ref23089" refString="Morley C. 1913 b. On Walker's Japanese Ichneumonidae. Entomologist. 46: 131 - 135." type="journal article" year="1913">Morley (1913b)</bibRefCitation>
suggested that 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1874" box="[797,950,737,762]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Lissonota" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semistriata">
<emphasis box="[797,950,737,762]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">L. semistriata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is related to or a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Panzer, 1809)" baseAuthorityName="Panzer" baseAuthorityYear="1809" box="[324,706,772,797]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Earinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gloriatorius">
<emphasis box="[324,535,772,797]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Earinus gloriatorius</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Panzer GWF" box="[551,697,772,797]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" pagination="8 - 10" refId="ref23408" refString="Panzer GWF. 1809. Faunae Insectorum Germanicae. Heft. 102: 14 - 22. 107: 8 - 10." type="journal article" year="1809">Panzer, 1809</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Townes HK &amp; Townes M &amp; Gupta VK" box="[719,884,772,797]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" pagination="1 - 522" refId="ref24468" refString="Townes HK, Townes M, Gupta VK. 1961. A catalogue and reclassification of the Indo-Australian Ichneumonidae. Mem Am Entomol Inst. 1: 1 - 522." type="journal article" year="1961">Townes (1961)</bibRefCitation>
transferred this species to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille, 1804 in Latreille" authorityYear="1805" box="[191,273,807,832]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Agathis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[191,273,807,832]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Agathis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<bibRefCitation author="Sharkey MJ" box="[336,501,807,832]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" pagination="1 - 100" refId="ref23632" refString="Sharkey MJ. 1996. The Agathidinae (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) of Japan. Bull Nat Inst Agro- Environmental Sci. 13: 1 - 100." type="journal article" year="1996">Sharkey (1996)</bibRefCitation>
then to 
<taxonomicName authority="Fabricius, 1804" authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1804" box="[599,845,807,832]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Bassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[599,671,807,832]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Bassus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Fabricius JC" box="[678,845,807,832]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" refId="ref21550" refString="Fabricius JC. 1804. Systema Piezatorum: secundum ordines, genera, species, adjectis synonymis, locis, observationibus, descriptionibus. Brunsvigae: Carolum Reichard; 439 + 32 pp." type="book" year="1804">Fabricius, 1804</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="68.[160,1156,879,974]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,291,879,905]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
We propose a new combination, 
<taxonomicName authority="(Walker, 1874)" authorityName="Shimizu &amp; Broad" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Walker" baseAuthorityYear="1874" box="[709,1156,880,905]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Therophilus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semistriatus" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[709,977,880,905]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Therophilus semistriatus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Walker F" box="[996,1148,880,905]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" pagination="301 - 310" refId="ref25043" refString="Walker F. 1874. Descriptions of some Japanese Hymenoptera. Cistula Entomol. 1: 301 - 310." type="journal article" year="1874">Walker, 1874</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[160,295,915,940]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,289,915,940]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">comb. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
, based on recent work splitting the old concept of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fabricius" authorityYear="1804" box="[910,982,915,940]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Bassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[910,982,915,940]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Bassus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(which is now restricted to a few species; e.g. 
<bibRefCitation author="Sharkey MJ &amp; Chapman EG" box="[514,854,949,974]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" pagination="49 - 72" refId="ref23660" refString="Sharkey MJ, Chapman EG. 2015. The Nearctic genera of Agathidinae (Hymenoptera: Braconidae) with a phylogenetic analysis, illustrated generic key, and the description of three new genera. Zootaxa. 4000: 49 - 72. doi: 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4000.1.2." type="journal article" year="2015">Sharkey and Chapman (2015))</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="68.[160,1156,1021,1082]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,389,1021,1047]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Current taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="(Walker, 1874)" authorityName="Shimizu &amp; Broad" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Walker" baseAuthorityYear="1874" box="[405,853,1022,1047]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Therophilus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semistriatus" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[405,674,1022,1047]" italics="true" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">Therophilus semistriatus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Walker F" box="[693,845,1022,1047]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" pagination="301 - 310" refId="ref25043" refString="Walker F. 1874. Descriptions of some Japanese Hymenoptera. Cistula Entomol. 1: 301 - 310." type="journal article" year="1874">Walker, 1874</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[866,1004,1022,1047]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[866,998,1022,1047]" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182">comb. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
(
<taxonomicName authorityName="Nees von Esenbeck" authorityYear="1811" box="[1023,1152,1022,1047]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Braconidae</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName box="[160,300,1057,1082]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="68" pageNumber="1182" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Agathidinae">Agathidinae</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
